{
  "texts": [
    "A new chat was started for each abstract generation to avoid the influence of previous commands and information.",
    "The prompt was based on the author guideline of a medical journal in which the RCT was published (see S1 Fig).",
    "These recommendations encompassed the word count limit and the required subheadings of the abstract.",
    "Moreover, after confirming ChatGPT's knowledge of the CONSORT-A, the model was instructed to adhere to the checklist during the abstract generation.",
    "Quality of the abstract was determined by assessing its adherence to the 18-item CONSORT-A checklist (see S2 Fig.)."
  ]
}